  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "What are some alternatives to yelp in India?",
  "response": "If you're looking for alternatives to Yelp in India for finding and reviewing local businesses, restaurants, and services, here are some popular options:\n\n1. **Zomato**\n   - **Overview:** Originally a restaurant discovery platform, Zomato has expanded to include reviews, menus, and online ordering.\n   - **Features:** Detailed restaurant profiles, user reviews and ratings, photos, reservation options, and delivery services in many cities.\n\n2. **TripAdvisor**\n   - **Overview:** A global platform widely used in India for travel-related content.\n   - **Features:** Reviews and ratings for restaurants, hotels, attractions, and experiences. Includes user photos and detailed descriptions.\n\n3. **Google Maps and Google Reviews**\n   - **Overview:** An essential tool for navigation and local business information.\n   - **Features:** Extensive user-generated reviews and ratings for a vast array of businesses, real-time updates, and integration with other Google services.\n\n4. **Justdial**\n   - **Overview:** A comprehensive local search engine in India.\n   - **Features:** Listings for businesses across various categories like restaurants, plumbers, electricians, and more, along with user reviews and contact information.\n\n5. **Dineout**\n   - **Overview:** A platform focused on dining experiences.\n   - **Features:** Restaurant discovery, user reviews, reservation services, exclusive deals, and discounts for dining out.\n\n6. **MouthShut**\n   - **Overview:** A consumer review platform covering a wide range of products and services.\n   - **Features:** Detailed reviews and ratings for restaurants, hotels, electronics, automobiles, and more, written by verified users.\n\n7. **Sulekha**\n   - **Overview:** A local services marketplace in India.\n   - **Features:** Listings for various services such as home services, events, wellness, and dining, along with user reviews and ratings.\n\n8. **Nearbuy (formerly Groupon India)**\n   - **Overview:** Focuses on discounts and deals for local businesses.\n   - **Features:** User reviews and ratings, along with exclusive offers and discounts for restaurants, spas, events, and more.\n\n9. **Facebook Pages and Reviews**\n   - **Overview:** Many businesses maintain active Facebook pages where customers can leave reviews.\n   - **Features:** User-generated reviews, ratings, photos, and direct interaction with business owners.\n\n10. **Swiggy (Swiggy Status)**\n    - **Overview:** Primarily a food delivery platform, Swiggy also offers features for restaurant reviews.\n    - **Features:** User ratings and reviews for restaurants, along with the ability to order food directly through the app.\n\n**Choosing the Right Platform:**\n- **Zomato and Swiggy** are excellent for food-related searches and reviews.\n- **Google Maps** provides a broad range of business reviews beyond just eateries.\n- **Justdial and Sulekha** are great for finding various local services with user feedback.\n- **TripAdvisor** is ideal if you're also interested in travel-related reviews.\n- **Dineout** is perfect for those looking to make reservations and find dining deals.\n\nEach platform has its unique strengths, so you might find it beneficial to use a combination of these services to get comprehensive information and reviews about businesses in India.",
